{"$ambrosia":"aero:interactive:9417ac60-5f60-11ea-8e69-affb2224d7e8:*","$id":"e917f2d0-44df-11ed-8a56-75ee9ad3b3a6","$workspaceId":"7fff47c0-44d6-11ed-bcef-d5307f42495c","$projectId":"86cb0040-44df-11ed-8442-dbcbc27803ca","annotations":[],"configSchemaVersion":"/pluginGenericSchema/v1","config":{"stage":{"sections":[{"rowsAreFullWidth":false,"backgroundImageUrl":"","rows":[{"columns":[{"stageElements":[{"type":"stage-element-text","value":{"object":"value","document":{"object":"document","data":{},"nodes":[{"object":"block","type":"heading-one","ref":"1862bb83-bab4-43a7-b835-6fec41a32f98","nodes":[{"object":"text","text":"1.5 The Stock Market","marks":[]}],"data":{}}]}},"config":{"cssClass":""},"ref":"b5d17500-c7de-44ed-a8ab-7afe86370d43"}]}]},{"columns":[{"stageElements":[{"type":"stage-element-text","value":{"object":"value","document":{"object":"document","data":{},"nodes":[{"object":"block","type":"paragraph","ref":"d266fb5c-9bb2-4897-96ed-4db471045b0d","nodes":[{"object":"text","text":"In ","marks":[]},{"object":"inline","type":"reference-link","ref":"ba1b3dd3-72f6-4602-9557-1a89177601ba","nodes":[{"object":"text","text":"Section 1.3","marks":[]}],"data":{"reference":"ea1a2b20-44e0-11ed-8442-dbcbc27803ca"}},{"object":"text","text":", we established the goal of the financial manager: to maximize the wealth of the owners, the stockholders. The value of the owners’ investments in the corporation is determined by the price of a share of the corporation’s stock. Corporations can be private or public. A private corporation has a limited number of owners and there is no organized market for its shares, making it hard to determine the market price of its shares at any point in time. A public corporation has many owners and its shares trade on an organized market, called a ","marks":[]},{"data":{"ref":"575868dd-731e-46db-9361-fff53d25a3ab","stage":{"ref":"4a09d568-98ce-4aa7-a573-6d61e2221177","sections":[{"ref":"fcd0905f-63d4-4ffe-9e55-fb711156e6e1","rows":[{"ref":"e3912443-ac55-49f4-ad17-0307d65e2b06","columns":[{"ref":"841c7d51-6dc0-4dc5-895b-b6a750c76e51","stageElements":[{"ref":"845c543d-76da-4061-a783-be5b29464ca8","type":"stage-element-text","value":{"object":"value","document":{"object":"document","data":{},"nodes":[{"object":"block","type":"button","ref":"bb957a96-4328-427d-8418-d7c47ba33f63","nodes":[{"object":"block","type":"paragraph","ref":"0a4784a7-b0b3-4adf-afbb-4eb023789c90","nodes":[{"object":"text","text":"Organized market on which the shares of many corporations are traded.","marks":[]}],"data":{}}],"data":{}}]}}}]}]}]}]}},"nodes":[{"object":"text","text":"stock market (or stock exchange or bourse)","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]}],"object":"inline","type":"key-term","ref":"b230771d-5d38-44e7-8470-8f9ce33b9966"},{"object":"text","text":". These markets provide ","marks":[]},{"object":"text","text":"liquidity","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]},{"object":"text","text":" for a company’s shares and determine the market price for those shares. An investment is ","marks":[]},{"data":{"ref":"cea425ec-dafe-4276-8e1a-f736034e952a","stage":{"ref":"345ba59b-14aa-4404-8f7c-f952764374de","sections":[{"ref":"b447a347-e69a-4ffc-bd64-d6f6deed64c7","rows":[{"ref":"c87dbe12-9891-4798-a08b-61ab52b9c6d5","columns":[{"ref":"013a530a-a9d0-4ed3-b138-7c37aa2864a5","stageElements":[{"ref":"3cbe9475-6370-4f70-9869-058f84fd242d","type":"stage-element-text","value":{"object":"value","document":{"object":"document","data":{},"nodes":[{"object":"block","type":"button","ref":"f1d8ad71-04af-4dab-b978-fa3b7c00bcda","nodes":[{"object":"block","type":"paragraph","ref":"f0094ca8-2c75-4ee0-a279-b1a07ef96834","nodes":[{"object":"text","text":"Describes an investment that can be easily turned into cash because it can be sold immediately at a competitive market price.","marks":[]}],"data":{}}],"data":{}}]}}}]}]}]}]}},"nodes":[{"object":"text","text":"liquid","marks":[{"type":"bold"}]}],"object":"inline","type":"key-term","ref":"c62a3294-e2dc-43c5-8ce3-c453301805ea"},{"object":"text","text":" if it can be easily turned into cash by selling it immediately at a competitive market price. An investor in a public company values the ability to turn his investment into cash easily and quickly by simply selling his shares on one of these markets. In this section, we provide an overview of the functioning of the major stock markets. The analysis and trading by participants in these markets provides an evaluation of the financial managers’ decisions that determines the stock price and provides essential feedback to the managers on their decisions.","marks":[]}],"data":{}}]}},"config":{"cssClass":""},"ref":"81c9c778-77ee-45ad-839e-7bd502821cb6"}]}]},{"columns":[{"stageElements":[{"type":"stage-element-image","config":{"url":{"$ambrosia":"aero:asset:upload","urn":"urn:aero:70bdbf80-44e0-11ed-9423-b5340f85eced","asset":{"urn":"urn:aero:70bdbf80-44e0-11ed-9423-b5340f85eced","asset":{"assetProvider":"ALFRESCO","id":"70bdbf80-44e0-11ed-9423-b5340f85eced","assetMediaType":"image","assetVisibility":"GLOBAL","ownerId":"e88133a0-8dc4-11eb-964e-4d7e264c9958","subscriptionId":"f0afd4d0-d2ff-11ea-9998-d57e1e28aca1","alfrescoId":"2899a541-a1a4-479a-bd47-319f7cd3cf5f","name":"PH_01_002.jpg","version":"2.0","lastModifiedDate":1664998397,"lastSyncDate":1665085917},"source":{"small":{"width":300,"url":"https://assets-bronte-qaint.pearson.com/70bdbf80-44e0-11ed-9423-b5340f85eced/small/c190766e39559eea28fe484001cb0300.jpeg","height":453},"original":{"width":300,"url":"https://assets-bronte-qaint.pearson.com/70bdbf80-44e0-11ed-9423-b5340f85eced/small/c190766e39559eea28fe484001cb0300.jpeg","height":453},"thumb":{"width":150,"url":"https://assets-bronte-qaint.pearson.com/70bdbf80-44e0-11ed-9423-b5340f85eced/thumb/c190766e39559eea28fe484001cb0300.jpeg","height":227}},"metadata":{"altText":"","workURN":"","caption":"","alfrescoPath":"bronte-e2e-testing-qaint/documentLibrary/BV E2E Test/[10-05-2022] Berk","originalAssetName":"PH_01_002.jpg","longDesc":"","hei